      "title": "[正面] Morimens is a very good roguelite card game with f...",
      "summary": "Morimens is a very good roguelite card game with fun mechanics ([i]e.g. the relics system or the symptom cards that you collect during runs[/i]) and beautiful artstyle.  Story is interesting and pretty well written compared to other titles of this sort, but sometimes there are issues with the translation ([i]which is understandable because it's partially done using AI[/i]). Although it's a gacha game, it's generous with the amount of free pulls for the standard and limited banners.\n😀👍",
